videos.description: One of the few concerns for No. 1 Alabama this offseason was the relative inexperience of its quarterbacks and running backs. But after a gutty win Saturday at No. 19 Ole Miss, Damien Harris and Jalen Hurts left few doubts moving forward.
videos.headline: Young Alabama backfield should inspire confidence
